1
00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I call first dibs!</font>

2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, not yet!</font>

3
00:00:04,670 --> 00:00:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready to pop some champagne?</font>

4
00:00:06,740 --> 00:00:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it!</font>

5
00:00:10,610 --> 00:00:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>Five Years Ago
New Year's Day</b></font></font></font></font>

6
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is starting to become 
our own little tradition.</font>

7
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank god. I'd rather be here 
than with my relatives.</font>

8
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same.</font>

9
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kotoko, pace yourself now.</font>

10
00:00:25,180 --> 00:00:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just getting started.</font>

11
00:00:27,580 --> 00:00:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, this looks good!</font>

12
00:00:29,210 --> 00:00:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm your biggest fan!</font>

13
00:00:30,390 --> 00:00:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whose?</font>

14
00:00:31,170 --> 00:00:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oysters.</font>

15
00:00:33,430 --> 00:00:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio, you haven't been home 
for New Year's in forever.</font>

16
00:00:36,630 --> 00:00:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, even outside of New Year's.</font>

17
00:00:39,140 --> 00:00:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My older sister's there
 with her kid a lot.</font>

18
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what about your guy? 
That Kasamachi fella.</font>

19
00:00:48,660 --> 00:00:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. We split up.</font>

20
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way.</font>

21
00:00:52,450 --> 00:00:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Why?</font>

22
00:00:58,170 --> 00:00:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

23
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get you.</font>

24
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh, uh-huh.</font>

25
00:01:03,410 --> 00:01:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, right. That was all gibberish.</font>

26
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno. He was too perfect. 
It was draining.</font>

27
00:01:09,050 --> 00:01:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Like he'd nitpick you about things?</font>

28
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, never.</font>

29
00:01:13,030 --> 00:01:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just felt stupid and got tired.</font>

30
00:01:17,530 --> 00:01:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be more specific.</font>

31
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need more drinks first.</font>

32
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, gang! It's New Year's!</font>

33
00:01:25,550 --> 00:01:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't anyone have any juicy updates?</font>

34
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

35
00:01:28,570 --> 00:01:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me neither! I'm never 
falling in love again.</font>

36
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You're not? Like ever?</font>

37
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never ever.</font>

38
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean it's set in stone?</font>

39
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, I decided recently.</font>

40
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rather, I had an epiphany.</font>

41
00:01:42,710 --> 00:01:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh man, an epiphany?</font>

42
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

43
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now everything in the past makes sense.</font>

44
00:01:50,110 --> 00:01:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All crystal clear?</font>

45
00:01:51,510 --> 00:01:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It is.</font>

46
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. She seemed willing to go today, so...</font>

47
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for the trouble.</font>

48
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>Present Day
November</b></font></font></font></font>

49
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'll see how she does
 for the time being.</font>

50
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, she has to process
things for herself.</font>

51
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

52
00:03:44,550 --> 00:03:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia">{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 9\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<font size="18">Intersect</font></font></font></font></font>

53
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, thank you.</font>

54
00:03:47,770 --> 00:03:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

55
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm drained...</font>

56
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole world feels noisy...</font>

57
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

58
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Asa-chan!</font>

59
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's finally back.</font>

60
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. It's been a while.</font>

61
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Takumi-san, I heard 
you caught a nasty cold.</font>

62
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:22,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Knocked me out for ten days.</font>

63
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could have ten days off!</font>

64
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="20"><font color="#e1e3d6">Musaka Band Club</font></font></font></font>

65
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="20"><font color="#e1e3d6">Winter Live Concert 2018</font></font></font></font>

66
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're working on fliers?</font>

67
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The job fell on us first-years
 without a place in the band.</font>

68
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing's changed for us 
since the school festival.</font>

69
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...</font>

70
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mimori-chan?</font>

71
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, she got picked while you were out.</font>

72
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's debuting with the second-year band.</font>

73
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

74
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, she's good, you know?</font>

75
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she's got stage presence.</font>

76
00:04:55,060 --> 00:05:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We either have to get really good at
 playing or write our own original songs.</font>

77
00:05:00,990 --> 00:05:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are they only ways to snag a spot.</font>

78
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Original songs...</font>

79
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They get priority as a rule, remember?</font>

80
00:05:08,450 --> 00:05:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, wanna do a run-through?</font>

81
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, please.</font>

82
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cool...</font>

83
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not fair.</i></font>

84
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, why can't we do that?</font>

85
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial"><font face="Impact"><font color="#393217">Counselor's Office</font></font></font></font></font>

86
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything you'd 
like to talk about?</font>

87
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

88
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

89
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be anything.</font>

90
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do people usually talk about?</font>

91
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything at all. There's no right answer.</font>

92
00:05:54,530 --> 00:05:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not fair. Screw this.</i></font>

93
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that something I'm supposed
 to come up with?</font>

94
00:06:04,930 --> 00:06:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's counseling good for, anyway?</font>

95
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's like, "Talk about anything."</font>

96
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't come up with anything.</font>

97
00:06:11,030 --> 00:06:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably because your
 head's always empty.</font>

98
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shaddup!</font>

99
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Counseling, huh?</font>

100
00:06:19,490 --> 00:06:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A guy from cram school told me 
he goes just to chat.</font>

101
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, he doesn't go to school much.</font>

102
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

103
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, who's this guy?</font>

104
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}There you go again. So annoying.</font>

105
00:06:30,590 --> 00:06:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it!</font>

106
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, spill!</font>

107
00:06:32,890 --> 00:06:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he your boyfriend?</font>

108
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have one now?</font>

109
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get off my case!</font>

110
00:06:36,410 --> 00:06:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not talking romance with you anymore.</font>

111
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why? How come? Tell me!</font>

112
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you're annoying.</font>

113
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Can you pick up some meat? Any kind."</font>

114
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any kind?</font>

115
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that Makio-san?</font>

116
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, she's been totally 
zoned out recently.</font>

117
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's wiped most of the time.</font>

118
00:06:56,050 --> 00:06:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because of work, I guess.</font>

119
00:06:58,100 --> 00:07:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Is being a novelist that hard?</font>

120
00:06:58,810 --> 00:07:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18"><font color="#191919">Got nothing in the tank.
Can't do anything else.</font></font></font></font>

121
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18"><font color="#191919">Get whatever meat you want.</font></font></font></font>

122
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

123
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she gets to do something she loves.</font>

124
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She even day drinks sometimes.</font>

125
00:07:07,990 --> 00:07:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

126
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope I get to do something I like too.</font>

127
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what?</font>

128
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno. It's impossible to know, right?</font>

129
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I wish someone would 
just choose for me.</font>

130
00:07:20,670 --> 00:07:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it wouldn't be something you love.</font>

131
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't know what I'm good at.</font>

132
00:07:28,210 --> 00:07:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#fefdfa">Seize your dreams with your talents</font></font></b></font></font>

133
00:07:28,210 --> 00:07:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's true.</font>

134
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you're good at writing
 like Makio-san.</font>

135
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

136
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows? You could be a genius!</font>

137
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just maybe!</font>

138
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The exit will be on your right.</i></font>

139
00:07:42,010 --> 00:07:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Attention passengers.</i></font>

140
