149
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="10"><font face="Arial"><font color="#4f504c"><font color="#0c0c0c">Bargain</font></font></font></font></font>

150
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="8"><font face="Arial"><font color="#4f504c"><font color="#0c0c0c">Domestic Chicken (Thighs)</font></font></font></font></font>

151
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, so...</font>

152
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

153
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Us first-years are all 
writing lyrics and...</font>

154
00:08:05,410 --> 00:08:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyrics?</font>

155
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the band.</font>

156
00:08:07,970 --> 00:08:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. What about the song?</font>

157
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No song yet.</font>

158
00:08:12,610 --> 00:08:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're starting with lyrics.</font>

159
00:08:14,810 --> 00:08:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean I can look?</font>

160
00:08:16,940 --> 00:08:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, lemme know what you think.</font>

161
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Let's see here...</font>

162
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's this rule that people who write 
songs get priority to perform on stage.</font>

163
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I only started it today, 
so I doubt it's good, but...</font>

164
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

165
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

166
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Wow... Okay...</font>

167
00:08:46,090 --> 00:08:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that reaction?!</font>

168
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, nothing. It's just so... 
young and fresh.</font>

169
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is this your first time
 writing lyrics?</font>

170
00:08:54,090 --> 00:08:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're totally weirded out!</font>

171
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on. Am I embarrassing myself?</font>

172
00:08:57,620 --> 00:09:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me I'll never live this down!</font>

173
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, don't worry about stuff like that.</font>

174
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's the time to write 
as much as you can.</font>

175
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm being serious when I say that.</font>

176
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I <i>am</i> embarrassing myself!</font>

177
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. Any tips?</font>

178
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gimme some advice.</font>

179
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

180
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

181
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First off, the main subject is unclear.</font>

182
00:09:20,290 --> 00:09:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's better to focus on one topic.</font>

183
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first half is about small details,</font>

184
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you could expand on that in the 
bridge to drive home your point.</font>

185
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And overall, your expressions 
are somewhat vague, so—</font>

186
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not like that!</font>

187
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

188
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

189
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if you concentrate on what 
you want to say most?</font>

190
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have anything I want to say.</font>

191
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, okay...</font>

192
00:09:58,410 --> 00:10:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else? Any other advice?</font>

193
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

194
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, well...</font>

195
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Write with the intent to kill.</font>

196
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strike, forge, and polish 
like your life is on the line.</font>

197
00:10:16,190 --> 00:10:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And stake your life on the kill.</font>

198
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what it means to write.</font>

199
00:10:26,130 --> 00:10:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What gives?</font>

200
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come you always talk weird like that?</font>

201
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like you're from another country.</font>

202
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then...</font>

203
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I have that back now?</font>

204
00:10:41,770 --> 00:10:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, can I keep it?</font>

205
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why?</font>

206
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It gives me strength.</font>

207
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! It needs more vocabulary!</font>

208
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vocabulary!</font>

209
00:10:50,950 --> 00:10:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's it, I bet.</font>

210
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that moment, I couldn't internalize 
what she was sharing with me.</i></font>

211
00:10:58,680 --> 00:11:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was like everyone was speaking 
to me in a foreign language.</i></font>

212
00:11:03,710 --> 00:11:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I wouldn't realize that 
until much later.</i></font>

213
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hcum os uoy evol I, rehtom ruoy sa, asA.</i></font>

214
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand any of it!</font>

215
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My aunt's a novelist, my parents 
are dead, and I've got it <i>so</i> hard!</font>

216
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have all the pieces 
to write some deep lyrics!</font>

217
00:11:23,490 --> 00:11:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why am I still so plain?!</font>

218
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was my biggest concern at the time.</i></font>

219
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>Asa's First Year
of High School</b></font></font></font></font>

220
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

221
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8"><font color="#c1bfb9">There's one last thing I need to tell you...</font></font></font></font>

222
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be nice.</font>

223
00:11:42,090 --> 00:11:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

224
00:11:43,780 --> 00:11:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want an epiphany too.</font>

225
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can say that again.</font>

226
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beat you to it.</font>

227
00:11:52,490 --> 00:11:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you.</font>

228
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>November 16th</b></font></font></font></font>

229
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I picked up a few things.</font>

230
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should last you a few days.</font>

231
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're spoiling her.</font>

232
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

233
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She didn't even come out to greet you.</font>

234
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, she messaged me.</font>

235
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Ten more lines," she said.</font>

236
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it'd be better for her 
if you were more strict.</font>

237
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:20,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, speaking from experience,</font>

238
00:12:20,090 --> 00:12:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not much good comes
 from treating anyone strictly.</font>

239
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, isn't it only natural 
to spoil someone you like?</font>

240
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:37,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Makio-san.</font>

241
00:12:38,570 --> 00:12:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you finish those ten lines?</font>

242
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you really are working hard.</font>

243
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought you some food.</font>

244
00:12:47,970 --> 00:12:49,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Like what?</font>

245
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's all prepped, so just sauté it....</font>

246
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, what if you reached out to someone?</font>

247
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For what?</font>

248
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignore me if you'd rather,</font>

249
00:12:58,530 --> 00:13:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I was thinking someone in your 
line of work might understand.</font>

250
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe help you out of this slump.</font>

251
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>November 27th</b></font></font></font></font>

252
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodness me!</font>

253
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my gosh, Juno-san!</font>

254
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}So you're in a slump, huh?</font>

255
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poor thing.</font>

256
00:13:16,810 --> 00:13:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me about it.</font>

257
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for having me.</font>

258
00:13:21,830 --> 00:13:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Hello.</font>

259
00:13:23,650 --> 00:13:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear she's taking care of you.</font>

260
00:13:25,620 --> 00:13:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that you need to be 
grateful or anything.</font>

261
00:13:29,370 --> 00:13:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koudai-san decided this
for herself, after all.</font>

262
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:32,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It all sounds swell!</font>

263
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Juno-san, is coffee okay?</font>

264
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

265
00:13:38,010 --> 00:13:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have some dorayaki, yeah?</font>

266
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

267
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in a big slump myself 
until a couple of years back.</font>

268
00:13:49,090 --> 00:13:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But you're constantly
pumping out new work.</font>

269
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it was three years ago or so...</font>

270
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could still write,
 but it all felt so bland.</font>

271
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bland?</font>

272
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how novelists are.</font>

273
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We frantically make stuff that 
we can guarantee is good, right?</font>

274
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And sometimes people give 
us that affirmative feedback.</font>

275
00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if that skews around 
people of a certain taste.</font>

276
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But nothing I made had any flavor to it.</font>

277
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing I wrote brought me joy.</font>

278
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was so lonely. I felt helpless.</font>

279
00:14:30,250 --> 00:14:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lonely...?</font>

280
00:14:32,190 --> 00:14:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very much so.</font>

281
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>December 20th</b></font></font></font></font>

282
00:14:35,570 --> 00:14:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow, she's actually day drinking.</font>

283
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got a problem?</font>

284
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finished my work.</font>

285
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's crazy.</font>

286
00:14:43,380 --> 00:14:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for having me over.</font>

287
00:14:45,530 --> 00:14:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe some luxury brand store?</font>

288
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm interested in architecture too.</font>

289
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Asa?</font>

290
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Live concert venues?</font>

291
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sounds cool!</font>

292
00:14:55,620 --> 00:14:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Makio-san?</font>

293
00:14:58,150 --> 00:15:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is being a novelist fulfilling?</font>

294
00:15:01,290 --> 00:15:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

295
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mother was a very sharp woman.</font>

296
00:15:06,790 --> 00:15:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If not for having a child,</font>

297
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or perhaps if she'd been born 
a generation later...</font>

298
00:15:13,070 --> 00:15:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I imagine she could've 
been someone important.</font>

299
00:15:17,430 --> 00:15:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I felt like...</font>

300
00:15:19,680 --> 00:15:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I stole my mother's life in a sense.</font>

301
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what, original sin?</font>

302
00:15:27,410 --> 00:15:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not on you. It's a societal flaw.</font>

303
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right you are!</font>

304
00:15:34,950 --> 00:15:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I landed my first job...</font>

305
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the bank?</font>

306
00:15:38,970 --> 00:15:39,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

307
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To no one's surprise, 
my dad wasn't impressed.</font>

308
00:15:45,410 --> 00:15:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Dad, I decided to accept 
the offer at the bank."</font>

309
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Is that so?"</font>

310
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your father really could be...</font>

311
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, right?</font>

312
00:15:55,310 --> 00:15:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when my mom heard, 
her ears turned bright red.</font>

313
00:15:59,090 --> 00:16:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said, "I think it's very admirable." 
Or something like that.</font>

314
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She used to work at the bank 
before they got married.</font>

315
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that was the only time 
she ever got visibly upset,</font>

316
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">now that I look back on it.</font>

317
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

318
00:16:16,450 --> 00:16:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, no! I hate my mom!</font>

319
00:16:19,250 --> 00:16:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said, "It feels like just yesterday
Emiri was pooping all over herself."</font>

320
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:26,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop making fun of me, Makio-san!</font>

321
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're laughing, but I'm sure you 
were in the same state back then.</font>

322
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ha, take that! Poopy Asa!</font>

323
00:16:35,140 --> 00:16:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah, there was this one recipe.</font>

324
00:16:37,730 --> 00:16:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In your mom's...</font>

325
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, her bento journal?</font>

326
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. It was potatoes and pickled
 plum wrapped in pork.</font>

327
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I wish I could have that again.</font>

328
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our work can feel futile.</font>

329
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like digging a hole, 
then filling it back up.</font>

330
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, Asa, did you decide about sci-lit?</font>

331
00:16:58,660 --> 00:17:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, not yet.</font>

332
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Sci-lit"?</font>

333
00:17:03,330 --> 00:17:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-san, have you been 
reading our handouts?</font>

334
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't... yet.</font>

335
00:17:08,620 --> 00:17:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not <i>yet</i>, huh?</font>

336
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're aiming for a national university?</font>

337
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd do science if I were 
better at math, but...</font>

338
00:17:14,780 --> 00:17:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you meant science or literature?</font>

339
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one did you choose, Makio-chan?</font>

340
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, literature, of course.</font>

341
00:17:21,170 --> 00:17:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, of course.</font>

342
00:17:21,930 --> 00:17:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

343
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I choose based on my career?</font>

344
00:17:26,360 --> 00:17:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or what I want to study at university?</font>

345
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'd tell you not to push 
yourself too hard, but...</font>

346
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not possible in your 
line of work, I suppose.</font>

347
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you decide to become 
a novelist, Makio-san?</font>

348
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just happened, I guess.</font>

349
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not an answer!</font>

350
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's be serious.</font>

351
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

352
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am being serious.</font>

353
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stay out of this.</font>

354
00:17:50,470 --> 00:17:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, whatcha writing, little one?</font>

355
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Little—</font>

356
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's self-conscious about her height.</font>

357
00:17:58,900 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I was talking about her age.</font>

358
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about that.</font>

359
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still growing!</font>

360
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares? I'm pretty short myself.</font>

361
00:18:08,610 --> 00:18:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's cute, don't you think?</font>

362
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

363
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to look good in wide-leg pants!</font>

364
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I have dorayaki now?!</font>

365
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

366
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, let's get along 
as fellow shorties.</font>

367
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I'm gonna become the 
person I want to be!</font>

368
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, even if you're boring or ordinary,</font>

369
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll find something you 
want to do eventually.</font>

370
00:18:32,730 --> 00:18:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's my own story.</font>

371
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People say our futures are boundless, 
which only gives me anxiety.</font>

372
00:18:40,290 --> 00:18:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person you want to be, huh?</font>

373
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's one for the ages!</font>

374
00:18:47,910 --> 00:18:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you...</font>

375
00:18:50,020 --> 00:18:53,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey now. Don't be rude like that.</font>

376
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Asa, right?</font>

377
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just picked a fight with the 
age-old question of humanity.</font>

378
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I just want to be free.</font>

379
00:19:02,470 --> 00:19:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry!</font>

380
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat, yeah?</font>

381
00:19:05,220 --> 00:19:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not too bad, actually.</font>

382
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All righty, let's whip something up.</font>

383
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get any of it.</i></font>

384
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not fair.</i></font>

385
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you.</i></font>

386
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not fair.</i></font>

387
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get any of it!</i></font>

388
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000"><b>December 19th</b></font></font></font></font>

389
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri's coming over tomorrow. 
Is that okay?</font>

390
00:19:57,190 --> 00:19:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

391
00:19:59,020 --> 00:20:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading out.</font>

392
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a good day.</font>

393
00:20:43,050 --> 00:20:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Done...!</font>

394
00:20:51,050 --> 00:20:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night.</font>

395
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I woke up in the middle 
of the night last night.</font>

396
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you cold? Do you need a heating pad?</font>

397
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should get to morning practice.</font>

398
00:21:21,910 --> 00:21:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, what happened 
with your lyrics?</font>

399
00:21:24,670 --> 00:21:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't bring that up.</font>

400
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not making fun of you.</font>

401
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really think you should give it a shot.</font>

402
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#75725a">November 27th</font></font></font></font>

403
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="16"><font color="#75725a">Juno-san</font></font></font></font>

404
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#75725a">I want to become the person I want to be!</font></font></font></font>

405
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off!</font>

406
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

407
00:21:43,710 --> 00:21:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a good day.</font>

408
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if I'll ever know...</i></font>

409
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>who I am, what I do and don't love,
 and how I'll live my life.</i></font>

410
00:21:57,210 --> 00:22:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe someday I'll figure it out.</i></font>

411
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someday...</i></font>

